sequenceDiagram
    participant C as CommitLog
    participant H as DefaultHAService
    participant G as GroupTransferService
    participant W as Master WriteSocketService
    participant S as Slave DefaultHAClient
    participant L as Slave CommitLog
    participant R as Master ReadSocketService

    C->>C: appendMessage
    C->>H: handleHA / putRequest
    H->>G: 等待目标 Offset
    W->>S: 发送 CommitLog 数据
    S->>L: appendToCommitLog
    S->>R: 上报最大复制 Offset
    R->>H: notifyTransferSome(offset)
    H->>G: 唤醒等待请求
    G-->>C: PUT_OK 或 FLUSH_SLAVE_TIMEOUT
